features: 20-count of individually wrapped pre-moistened Neutrogena Makeup Remover Wipe Singles. Individually wrapped facial towelettes are protected from drying out so you always have a fresh and effective wipe for complete cleansing and makeup removal

Makeup remover face cleansing towelettes work to dissolve all traces of dirt, remove bacteria, impurities, oil and makeup on skin while also removing pollution, sweat and sunscreen, for superior cleansing and makeup removing power at your fingertips

Facial cleansing wet wipes are ophthalmologist-, dermatologist-, and allergy-tested and gentle around the eye area. The effective formula removes up to 99% of makeup--even stubborn waterproof mascara--without tugging

body.description: Cleanse skin and remove makeup in one easy step with Neutrogena Makeup Remover Face Wipes. These soft and gentle pre-moistened facial cleansing wipes effectively dissolve all traces of dirt, oil and makeup--even waterproof mascara-- for clean, fresh looking skin every day. Our waterproof makeup remover features an effective micellar-infused, triple emollient formula that leaves skin feeling refreshed, nourished, conditioned and refreshingly clean with no heavy residue. These cleansing facial towelettes also remove sweat, sunscreen, and pollution from skin with no need to rinse after use. These daily face wipes are formulated to be gentle on the sensitive eye area. The makeup removing wet wipes are formulated without phthalates, parabens, sulfates, alcohols, soaps, or dyes and are ophthalmologist-, dermatologist-, and allergy-tested

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Reliable Choice for Quick and Effective Makeup Removal
reviews.reviewText: I recently tried the Neutrogena Makeup Remover Wipes, and I must say they have become a staple in my daily skincare routine. As someone with sensitive skin, finding a makeup remover that is both gentle and effective has always been a challenge. Neutrogena's offering, however, pleasantly surprised me.The first thing that stood out to me was the convenience of the packaging. The resealable closure ensures that the wipes stay moist and ready to use, making them perfect for on-the-go makeup removal or late-night skincare routines when you just want something quick and efficient.These wipes boast an impressive ability to remove makeup, even stubborn waterproof mascara and long-lasting lipsticks. With just one wipe, I found myself able to completely cleanse my face of makeup without excessive rubbing or irritation. The formula is gentle on the skin, leaving it feeling refreshed and not overly dry or greasy.One of the key features I appreciate about these wipes is their non-comedogenic nature. As someone prone to occasional breakouts, it's reassuring to know that the product won't clog pores or contribute to skin issues. The absence of any heavy fragrance is also a plus for those with sensitivities to scented products.What makes these wipes stand out is the addition of the patented Neutrogena cleansing technology. It not only removes makeup but also effectively cleanses the skin, leaving it feeling soft and nourished. I noticed a difference in the texture of my skin after regular use – it felt smoother and looked healthier.While the wipes are excellent for everyday use, they are particularly handy during travel. The compact packaging takes up minimal space in my toiletry bag, and I can trust that I have a reliable makeup remover with me wherever I go.In summary, Neutrogena Makeup Remover Wipes have earned a permanent spot in my skincare routine. They deliver on their promise of effective makeup removal without compromising on skin health. If you're in search of a reliable, gentle, and convenient makeup remover, these wipes are definitely worth trying.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just wow! Small pack, large wipe that gets it all!
reviews.reviewText: This pack is so small it fits anywhere. But when you unwrap it, it's almost as big as a wash cloth and easily removes all of the makeup without drying the skin. I'm a fan! Great price and arrived quickly. 👏

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very convenient for traveling
reviews.reviewText: These are much easier to travel with than carrying around the larger packages (if we are only going for a few days, we don't need to take a package with 25, 50, or 100 of them inside). They get the job done and work the same.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Hands down the best
reviews.reviewText: Neutrogena wipes fight all stubborn makeup without irritating your skin. I’ve used these religiously for the last 16 years or longer and will never give them up. They’re convenient, fragrance-free, non-irritating, and easy to use. No water necessary and can be used on the go.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great for traveling
reviews.reviewText: After reading a travel blog, I bought these for a trip to Hawaii to try out as my makeup eraser doesn’t get all the mascara out. The napkin cloth is well saturated and removes makeup, but didn’t quite get all the mascara (perhaps user error?), so I used my travel sized makeup eraser cloth and this napkin cloth and I was able to remove all the mascara. The napkin feels nice and soft on the skin. It left what felt like a moisturizing film on my skin which (which I didn’t like), but after washing my face with my usual cleanser (Cetaphil), my skin felt wonderful! Had it removed all mascara I would give it 5 stars.
